divs: sighting detailsa findlay, oh real estate agent may have accidentaly caught a ufo on film. the exact date and time of the photograph is not known, but was taken sometime in the last three weeks. after the photos were taken and stitched together for a "virtual tour" of the outside of the property, an anomoly was noticed in the sky on one of the photos. the photo can be viewed via realtor.com at the following link: http:\\www.realtor.com\prop\1048943090?lnksrc=00045 click on the "virtual tour" button and select the "deck \ back yard" button. the object can be seen in the view looking back across the back yard over the corn field. there is another object that can be seen over the roofline of the house but this is thought to be a pole light.
Summary: UFO accidentally caught in photo by real estate agent
